#########################
# Code Base of this Mod #
#########################
The code is based on a tutorial published by Thunderseb on the French site "Le site du Zéro": http://www.siteduzero.com/tutoriel-3-34703-insertion-de-balises-dans-une-zone-de-texte.html

####################
# Custom icons set #
####################
The icons are based on the Tango icons set: http://tango.freedesktop.org/Tango_Icon_Library

